  "detailed_description": "The game takes place in an abandoned mansion in the suburbs after an underground party. You wake up alone and lost, finding the place deserted and immersed in darkness. In your search through the somber chambers you perceive a sinister presence that haunts you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/cdd217b5f587cdf53fc1faed01dd94f1.poster.avif?t=1729784514\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/cdd217b5f587cdf53fc1faed01dd94f1.webm?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/cdd217b5f587cdf53fc1faed01dd94f1.mp4?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Equipped with a lamp and a lighter to help you illuminate your path, you must scavenge for resources to unlock new areas before it is too late to escape the mansion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a3f473269b11b93b5e132b494b2d88f4.poster.avif?t=1729784514\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a3f473269b11b93b5e132b494b2d88f4.webm?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a3f473269b11b93b5e132b494b2d88f4.mp4?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Intricate rooms are randomly generated ensuring a novel and tense experience on each playthrough.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a1f9324265d130465ae6d135adda49fb.poster.avif?t=1729784514\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a1f9324265d130465ae6d135adda49fb.webm?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a1f9324265d130465ae6d135adda49fb.mp4?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The game takes place in an abandoned mansion in the suburbs after an underground party. You wake up alone and lost, finding the place deserted and immersed in darkness. In your search through the somber chambers you perceive a sinister presence that haunts you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/cdd217b5f587cdf53fc1faed01dd94f1.poster.avif?t=1729784514\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/cdd217b5f587cdf53fc1faed01dd94f1.webm?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/cdd217b5f587cdf53fc1faed01dd94f1.mp4?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Equipped with a lamp and a lighter to help you illuminate your path, you must scavenge for resources to unlock new areas before it is too late to escape the mansion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a3f473269b11b93b5e132b494b2d88f4.poster.avif?t=1729784514\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a3f473269b11b93b5e132b494b2d88f4.webm?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a3f473269b11b93b5e132b494b2d88f4.mp4?t=1729784514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Intricate rooms are randomly generated ensuring a novel and tense experience on each playthrough.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981840/extras/a1f9